Third-Party Software and Assets
================================

The authoritative dependency and asset inventory for the current lockfiles is:

  docs/THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.md
  artifacts/THIRD-PARTY-LICENSES.json
  artifacts/sbom/frontend.cdx.json
  artifacts/sbom/rust.cdx.json
  artifacts/sbom/skill-studio-pro.cdx.json

These files preserve package-declared license expressions and evidence. A
missing or unknown license is a CI failure; the project does not guess license
terms. Components remain under their respective licenses. Attribution or
file-level obligations identified by the generated inventory continue to apply
to those components.

Brand and Icon Assets
=====================

The Skill Studio Pro mark, wordmark, and generated application icons are
original project artwork distributed under Apache-2.0. Upstream Skill Studio
logo files are retained only under branding/upstream-logo-reference/ for
attribution and audit and are excluded from the formal Pro application brand.

Third-party platform names and brands, including Codex, Claude Code, Cursor,
Windsurf, and Gemini CLI, are owned by their respective holders. Their names
are used only for identification and interoperability and do not imply
endorsement, sponsorship, or affiliation.

No font files are bundled. Runtime UI font stacks use fonts supplied by the
user's operating system.
